*&quot;The Book of Small&quot;. Vancouver: Douglas &amp; McIntyre, 2004;
*&quot;The Heart of a Peacock&quot;. Vancouver: Douglas &amp; McIntyre, 2005;
*&quot;The House of All Sorts&quot;. Vancouver: Douglas &amp; McIntyre, 2004;

== Writing by Carr edited by other authors ==
