<doc id="290625" wikidata="Q5519973" url="?curid=290625" title="Game six">
<text>Game six is a shorthand reference to a sixth game of a sports playoff series. Several World Series have had sixth games that were especially memorable, and were referred to by this shorthand expression. Some of them are:

*1975 World Series
*1985 World Series
*1986 World Series
*1992 World Series
*1993 World Series
*2011 World Series

